OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly morning low cloud will
OL,6,Fgradually dissipate to give sunny
OL,7,Fspells for most areas, low cloud
OL,8,Flikely lingering along the coast
OL,9,Fthroughout the day. Feeling warm in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine, cooler along the coast
OL,11,Fwith an onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA clear evening for most.
OL,14,FOvernight, low cloud will spread
OL,15,Finland from the North Sea, affecting
OL,16,Fmany areas by dawn. Staying dry for
OL,17,Fmost, with a light northeasterly
OL,18,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
